    <summary>Introduction</summary>
    <p>Hello! My name is Juriヾ(´･ ･｀)ノ”</p><p>I have a dream that, when my mind becomes quiet, I will spend my life simply and contentedly.</p><p>I wanted to create a place to call home for the world inside of my head.<p>Thank you!</p>
</details>
            <details class="mydetails">
    <summary>Planet</summary>
    <p>It is described as a different planet here, as I often feel like a stranger on Earth and wish that I could live on a planet of my own, all on my own.</p><p>The theme is also inspired by one of my favorite novels, <i>The Little Prince</i>, whose titular character meets various characters on different planets and on Earth.</p>
</details></div>
